'''肾综合征出血热'''（hemorrhagic fever with renal syndrome，'''HFRS'''）是一种主要由[[鼠类|鼠类]]携带[[汉坦病毒|汉坦病毒]]引起的自然疫源性疾病。引起肾综合征出血热的[[病毒|病毒]]主要有[[汉滩病毒|汉滩病毒]](HTNV)、[[汉城病毒|汉城病毒]](SEOV)、[[普马拉病毒|普马拉病毒]](PUUV)和[[多不拉伐病毒|多不拉伐病毒]](DOBV)等<ref name="biods.2020264">{{cite journal |last1=Hou |first1=Xiang |last2=Feng |first2=Tuo |last3=Han |first3=Ning |last4=Wang |first4=Jing |last5=Chen |first5=Xiaoning |last6=An |first6=Xiaolei |last7=Xu |first7=Lei |last8=Liu |first8=Qiyong |last9=Chang |first9=Gang |title=Effect of climate change and economic development on hemorrhagic fever with renal syndrome |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2020-10-20 |volume=28 |issue=10 |pages=1229 |doi=10.17520/biods.2020264}}</ref>。临床症状主要有[[发热|发热]]、[[出血|出血]]、[[头痛|头痛]]、[[低血压休克|低血压休克]]及[[肾脏|肾脏]]损害等<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Sargianou |first1=Maria |last2=Watson |first2=Dionysios Christos |last3=Chra |first3=Paraskevi |last4=Papa |first4=Anna |last5=Starakis |first5=Ioannis |last6=Gogos |first6=Charalambos |last7=Panos |first7=George |title=Hantavirus infections for the clinician: From case presentation to diagnosis and treatment |journal=Critical Reviews in Microbiology |date=2012-11-01 |volume=38 |issue=4 |pages=317–329 |doi=10.3109/1040841X.2012.673553 |pmid=22553984}}</ref>。传播通过接触宿主动物的[[排泄物|排泄物]]、[[伤口感染|伤口感染]]、[[气溶胶|气溶胶]], 还可通过[[螨类|螨类]]等传播或通过母体垂直传播<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Nichol |first1=S. T. |last2=Spiropoulou |first2=C. F. |last3=Morzunov |first3=S. |last4=Rollin |first4=P. E. |last5=Ksiazek |first5=T. G. |last6=Feldmann |first6=H. |last7=Sanchez |first7=A. |last8=Childs |first8=J. |last9=Zaki |first9=S. |last10=Peters |first10=C. J. |title=Genetic identification of a hantavirus associated with an outbreak of acute respiratory illness |journal=Science |date=1993-11-05 |volume=262 |issue=5135 |pages=914–917 |doi=10.1126/science.8235615 |pmid=8235615}}</ref>。欧亚大陆是肾综合征出血热的主要传播地区，死亡率为12%<ref name="biods.2020264" />。

